rComments: Professor Chiao is very professional, explains the material well and is very sweet. He has clear grading criteria, is flexible and is very accommodating to students. Really enjoyed taking his class!

Professor Chiao was friendly and respectful, and willing to help students if approached.  I appreciated his sense of humor. However, the material was not explained very well (possibly because he shys away from the lecturing format) and he used the same exam as the other professor teaching legal process. I would avoid taking classes with him.
Chiao is a really unclear teacher. He makes everything seem vastly more complicated than it should be.
